    "This also suggests a growing interest and possibly an increasing recognition of the importance of machine learning in AML practices.",
    "The result also reveals that conference papers outnumber journal papers in the earlier years (2019-2021), but the trend starts to balance out in 2022 and 2023.",
    "This shift could indicate a maturing research field, where more substantial and in-depth studies are being published in journals.",
    "Table 4.1: Publication trend Year Journal Paper Conference Paper Total 2019 0 1 1 2020 1 4 5 2021 3 6 9 2022 4 9 13 2023 9 15 24 Total 17 35 52",
